metadata.name: Nightmares.
metadata.description:
When I saw this scenery, in a first moment, I remembered of Guernica and Pablo Picasso, but soon after I remembered of a frequent nightmare that I used to have when I was a child: gigantic monsters ran through the city and devoured people. This must be the place where, in the interior of the human mind, all of them come together to agree on how they will scary us.
